title: Week 14 Recap 2021
description:
Field Yates, Matthew Berry, Stephania Bell and Kyle Soppe recap the key takeaways from Week 14 including a few passionate takes you have to hear. Plus, we talk who you can trust in the fantasy playoffs and preview Monday Night Football.
